com.siperian.sif.message

Class RecordState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.RecordState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RecordState
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class represents record states that can be assigned to a base object record in the Siperian Hub. Each record state has a unique name and a corresponding value.
    See Also:
